{"tid":1364524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗黑社會真係惡到仆街","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:25:14.000Z","uid":74778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64ec715cad3a391a28c5746e0ee287487931cf8c","tid":1364524,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"打撚完人，巿民入去遊行，抗議下，...<br />\n<br />\n屌佢班老味，佢地仲要劉業強出黎開記招講撚到明 <strong>你地入黎就入黎，踩到我條尾我一樣打撚爆你，我話你聽啊，我地全部務農，用咩㗎撐自衛我唔擔保</strong><br />\n<br />\n乜撚野言論？<br />\n<br />\n我當打人單野唔撚關你鄉議會事，你老味你咪彈開囉，開乜野記招<br />\n<br />\n你開記招，講撚定點反擊，係咪星期日單野關你事啊？關你事咁叫咩反擊啊？呢d叫巿民反擊啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地d嘴臉真係好撚閪<br />\n<br />\n由丁權開始，成日講d野都成個無賴咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzxdjnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzxdjnM.png&h=b1185215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖"},{"pid":"19676ab2ed8c6f63782aad6906650d81fa65e637","tid":1364524,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"我做廚房既，我用咩反擊都唔擔保喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecff308530b547d302fae88113e035f04100688","tid":1364524,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"我做地盤嘅，唔擔保會用咩黎還擊"},{"pid":"45c1bdf9ecb1b105056ba817d3aeed97dd3ce906","tid":1364524,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.dehua.net/info/upload/2005_03/050305195988133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.dehua.net%2Finfo%2Fupload%2F2005_03%2F050305195988133.jpg&h=5239de9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd6d34bbd84bbe85b9c1465824402f10f136518f","tid":1364524,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3ac4083c8cf3b5e3c5815e5b81d0d1f1527df487","tid":1364524,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"元朗反黑遊行因為警察害怕黑社會而取消了<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李鵬悼念會</strong></span>在元朗舉行<br />\n毌忘李同志遺願:<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究警黑勾結、濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTbYvJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTbYvJD.png&h=655c15f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*完成悼念後可以各自在元朗大馬路購物、品嚐元朗美食*<br />\n溫馨提示：可以在元朗站乘搭交通工具離開元朗市"},{"pid":"63b8866520490456867fe61ec5b8498649b903ad","tid":1364524,"uid":261505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:13:58.000Z","msg":"D牛屎佬無一個係無辜既"},{"pid":"51c22c7fe30013825cf6da8687f1fa651f6850c5","tid":1364524,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"727元朗捉精靈"},{"pid":"ffaa22c8963890dc213cce9c447da8ae0263944c","tid":1364524,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"我玩開War game"},{"pid":"049602c239c593f3cf9edaf435e209e87370d5b0","tid":1364524,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"𨳒你老母鄉黑牛屎佬，你班子侄件件廢青肥豬大食懶，耕田個鋤頭係㸃都未掂過，你舞個鋤頭我睇，舞兩野就去元朗沖涼揼骨! 牛屎佬的田都變貨櫃場，變你老母塊田就有份!"},{"pid":"c5f2c92685aa20fd5a5f172f98262076ab407232","tid":1364524,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049602c239c593f3cf9edaf435e209e87370d5b0","tid":1364524,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"𨳒你老母鄉黑牛屎佬，你班子侄件件廢青肥豬大食懶，耕田個鋤頭係㸃都未掂過，你舞個鋤頭我睇，舞兩野就去元朗沖涼揼骨! 牛屎佬的田都變貨櫃場，變你老母塊田就有份!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim